A 26-year-old Zimbabwean man was arrested after he was caught pretending to be his girlfriend so that he could write her final exam on her behalf.
Mkonzi Mbango disguised himself as a woman and pretended to be his girlfriend so that he could write her exam for her. According to Mbango, he wanted to help his girlfriend because she was failing. After people noticed that Mbango was not a female, they alerted the necessary parties and dragged Mbango out of the classroom. He was then arrested. ~